                                            </div>
                                            <div style="background-image: url('https://www.busit.co.nz/assets/Busit/beecard-images/bee-card__ResizedImageWzMwMCwxODld.png');background-size: cover;width: 158px;height: 100px;margin: auto;border-radius: 8px;">
